<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.3.1">
<l>viṟperu viḻavuṅ kañcaṉum mallum vēḻamum pākaṉum vīḻa</l>
<l>ceṟṟavaṉ ṟaṉṉai purameri ceyta civaṉuṟu tuyarkaḷai tēvai</l>
<l>paṟṟalar vīyak kōlkaiyil koṇṭu pārttaṉṟaṉ tērmuṉiṉ ṟāṉai</l>
<l>ciṟṟavai paṇiyāl muṭituṟan tāṉait tiruvallik kēṇi<supplied>k</supplied>kaṇ ṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who destroyed the great festival bow, Kaṁsa, the wrestlers,</l>
<l rend="indent">an elephant, and the driver so they died,</l>
<l>The god who removed the suffering felt by Śiva who set fire to cities,</l>
<l>The one who stood at the front of Pārtha’s chariot bearing a whip in hand,</l>
<l rend="indent">so [his] enemies died,</l>
<l>The one who renounced [his] crown by order of a young woman,</l>
<l rend="indent">I saw at Tiruvallikkēṇi.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
